Privacy Policy
Last updated: August 29, 2024
Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our Wear OS watchface apps.
If you choose to use our Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. The Personal Information that we collect is used for providing and improving the Service. We will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
The terms used in this Privacy Policy have the same meanings as in our Terms and Conditions, which are accessible in our applications unless otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy.
Information Collection and Use
Our Wear OS watchface apps do not collect, store, or share any personal data. We do not require any permissions that involve accessing sensitive information, such as location, contacts, or messages.
Fitness Data
Our Wear OS watchface apps may collect data from body sensors to display your heart rate and step count. This information is gathered solely for the purpose of showing it on the watchface, and we do not store, share, or use this data for any other purpose.
Third-Party Services
Our apps do not use any third-party services that could collect or process your data.
Log Data
We want to inform you that whenever you use our Service, in the case of an error in the app, we collect data and information (through third-party products) on your phone called Log Data. This Log Data may include information such as the operating system version, the configuration of the app when utilizing our Service, the time and date of your use of the Service, and other statistics.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
We advise you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at
support@photogallerytv.com
.
